      "raw_text": "at $1120. and one valued at $1,000\nhave been found on this property. but\nthe one recently taken out is the\nlargest ever shown here. Two mug\ngets valued at over 500 each have\nalso been found there this season.\n\n\nThe ground of the company was\nrecently inspected by government\nexpert and was found to go from so\ncents to SLIPS per cubic yard.\n\n\nConsiderable difficulty has been ex-\nperienced this season, the water sup\nply being very limited, and in conse-\nquence the placer has been but little\nworked. A ditch is being built to\ncarry the water to the works and\nwhen this is completed the Cedar\nValley company will operate it's\nclaim on a larger scale"
